---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Backflow Testing & Certification" description="Licensed backflow testing and certification for irrigation systems in central Indiana. Stay compliant and protect your water supply with Allen Irrigation Company.">
  <Hero
    title="Backflow Testing & Certification"
    subtitle="Protect your drinking water and stay code-compliant"
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504328345606-18bbc8c9d7d1?w=1920&q=80"
    compact
  />

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">What Is Backflow Testing?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6">Your irrigation system connects directly to your home or business's potable water supply. A backflow prevention device ensures that water from your sprinkler system can't flow backward into your drinking water â€” protecting your family or customers from contaminated water.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6">Many Indiana municipalities require annual backflow testing and certification to verify your device is working correctly. Failure to test can result in fines or having your water service shut off.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Allen Irrigation provides professional backflow testing, repair, and replacement services. We handle the testing, paperwork, and submission to your local water utility so you don't have to worry about a thing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cover bg-center rounded-lg h-96" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160607-ee22621dd758?w=800&q=80')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">Our Backflow Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
        {[
          { icon: 'ðŸ“‹', title: 'Annual Testing & Certification', desc: 'We test your backflow preventer using calibrated gauges, complete the required paperwork, and submit results to your water utility.' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ”§', title: 'Repair & Rebuilds', desc: 'If your device fails the test, we can repair or rebuild it on the spot in most cases â€” saving you the cost and hassle of a return visit.' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ”„', title: 'Replacement & Installation', desc: 'For devices that are beyond repair or outdated, we install new backflow preventers that meet current Indiana code requirements.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
            <span class="text-4xl mb-4 block">{item.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-green-dark mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">How often do I need backflow testing?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Most Indiana water utilities require annual testing. We recommend scheduling it during your <a href="/services/spring-startup" class="text-green-mid hover:text-green-dark underline">spring startup</a> for convenience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">What happens if my backflow device fails?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">In most cases, we can repair or rebuild the device during the same visit. If a full replacement is needed, we'll provide an estimate and schedule the work promptly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">Do I really need a backflow preventer?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. Indiana plumbing code requires backflow prevention on all irrigation system connections. Beyond the legal requirement, it's essential for protecting your drinking water from fertilizers, pesticides, and other contaminants.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule Backflow Testing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner title="Due for Backflow Testing?" subtitle="Contact us to schedule your annual test and stay compliant." />
</BaseLayout>
